<ptxt>The correct waveform is as shown.</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<list1 type="unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>VV1+ and VV2+ stand for the VVT sensor signal, and NE+ stands for the CKP sensor signal.</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</atten4>
